## How {{ADR_COUNT}} ADRs depend on, refine, supersede, or conflict with each other

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    {{#ADRS}}
    {{id}}["<b>ADR-{{id}}</b><br/>{{title}}<br/><i>{{status}}</i>"]:::{{status_class}}
    {{/ADRS}}

    {{#ALL_RELATIONS}}
    {{#is_supersedes}}{{from_id}} -.->|"supersedes"| {{target_id}}{{/is_supersedes}}
    {{#is_refines}}{{from_id}} -->|"refines"| {{target_id}}{{/is_refines}}
    {{#is_depends_on}}{{from_id}} -->|"depends on"| {{target_id}}{{/is_depends_on}}
    {{#is_conflicts_with}}{{from_id}} ===|"⚠ conflict"| {{target_id}}{{/is_conflicts_with}}
    {{/ALL_RELATIONS}}

    classDef accepted fill:#d6f5d6,stroke:#2e8b2e,color:#222
    classDef proposed fill:#f0f0f0,stroke:#666,color:#222
    classDef superseded fill:#e0e0e0,stroke:#999,color:#666,stroke-dasharray:3 3
    classDef rejected fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c23838,color:#666,stroke-dasharray:3 3
    classDef deprecated fill:#ffe4b5,stroke:#c8740a,color:#444
```

