### What this diagram deliberately does *not* show

- **The actual decision content** — open the linked ADR file to read
  Decision / Consequences / Alternatives.
- **Implementation status** — an Accepted ADR is not necessarily shipped;
  this diagram is decision-graph only.
- **Open questions** — those live in the canvas § Open Questions
  fields, not in ADR relations.

