## Legend

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| 🟢 Green node | Accepted — current decision in force |
| ⬜ Grey node | Proposed — under deliberation, not yet binding |
| ⬛ Dashed grey | Superseded — historical, kept for traceability |
| 🟥 Dashed red | Rejected — explicitly turned down, kept to prevent re-litigation |
| 🟧 Amber | Deprecated — being phased out but not yet superseded |
| Solid arrow | Active relation: `refines` or `depends on` |
| Dashed arrow | Historical relation: `supersedes` (points to the older decision) |
| Bold `===` edge | `⚠ conflict` — known tension between two ADRs |

